This reproducibility report provides details about the artifact evaluation done with regards to the Artifact Description and Evaluation appendix of SC25 paper “MLP-Offload: Multi-Level, Multi-Path Offloading for LLM Pre-training to Break the GPU Memory Wall” by Avinash Maurya, et al. The work was done as part of the Reproducibility Initiative of SC25. The author is a member of the SC25 Reproducibilty Committee.